function [fitresult, gof] = createFit(cdate, pop)
%CREATEFIT(CDATE,POP)
%  Create a fit.
%
%  Data for 'poly6' fit:
%      X Input : cdate
%      Y Output: pop
%  Output:
%      fitresult : a fit object representing the fit.
%      gof : structure with goodness-of fit info.
